library(nlmixr2)

one_cpt_model <- function() {
  ini({
    t.KA <- -0.8 # Ka
    t.Q <- 1.2 # Q
    t.CL <- 2 # CL
    t.VC <- 2 # Vc
    t.VP <- 2 # Cp
    t.ALAG1 <- -0.1
    
    eta.CL ~ 0.1 # IIV on CL
    eta.VC ~ 0.1 # IIV on Vc
    
    add.sd <- 0.7  
  })
  
  model({
    KA = exp(t.KA)
    Q = exp(t.Q)
    CL = exp(t.CL + eta.CL)
    VC = exp(t.VC + eta.VC)
    VP = exp(t.VP)
    ALAG1 = exp(t.ALAG1)
    
    linCmt() ~ add(add.sd)
  })
}

nif.poppk <- nif.001 %>% 
  filter(FASTED == T) %>%
  filter(ANALYTE == \M1774\") %>%
